scene.message:
Tamaki: Hey! Why'd you go{nl}
messing up the clubroom!{nl}
Tadashi, you idiot!{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Aah, can't hear ya.{nl}
It's our room, our call.{nl}
Sheesh, fuming every day.{waitkey}You ugly Tamaki!{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: What did you say!{nl}
I'm tearing this trash down{nl}
right now!{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: Goddess my foot!{nl}
You perv! Perv perv{nl}
perv perv perv!{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Gah! You ugly hag!{nl}
Ugly ugly ugly ugly{nl}
ugly ugly ugly!{waitkey}{ret}

Club member: Ugh, these two.{nl}
Every single day with this.{nl}
Don't they ever get tired?{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: Huff, huff, huff...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
What is it?{nl}
I'm busy right now.{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Wheeze, wheeze...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
What do you want?{nl}
I'm busy right now.{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Tamaki{nl}
A transfer student in the{nl}
fencing club. She fights with{nl}
Tadashi every day.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Tadashi{nl}
A slacker in the fencing{nl}
club. He fights with Tamaki{nl}
every day.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Honestly, the idiots{nl}
in our athletic clubs...{nl}
utterly without restraint.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Weak paint job. If{nl}
you're gonna bomb graffiti,{nl}
you gotta put more into it!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Leave 'em be.{nl}
They say the more you fight,{nl}
the closer you are, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Female member: Tamaki's a{nl}
transfer, but she's good -{nl}
placed 3rd at a tournament.{waitkey}{clearbox}But she doesn't like talking{nl}
about her old school. Wonder{nl}
if something happened.{waitkey}{ret}
